title: 3v3 Tournament
body:
Hey Summoners, *Tournament! Alert* {{sticker:poppy-wink}} 

Got some spare time this Sunday? Get your groups together and join us for our 3v3 Twisted Treeline Tournament!

Please post below if you would like to form a team or you need someone.
